By accepting the Agreement, you **agree to indemnify and otherwise hold harmless** Us as well as Our officers, employees, agents, subsidiaries, affiliates, and other partners from any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or exemplary damages arising out of, relating to, or resulting from your use of Pruvious or any other matter relating to Pruvious. This paragraph also applies to you if you are not the licensee (e.g., if You use Pruvious while someone else is the licensee).

